column5: Hey Simon .... you should get up to this lake next winter, its still there waiting for you ....   http://outdoorcanada.ca/28879/news/articles/ontario-saskatchewan-produce-record-book-lake-trout-and-elk
wow !!! a huge fish,and a huge elk !!! what are they feeding them critters up there....awesome
I'll be on that lake this summer, can't wait!
Wow, big creatures.  Kudos to the angler for releasing that brute, many would not be able to do that.  I'd love to have a shot at the elk with a different weapon - a good camera!
